drm: Merge CONFIG_DRM_VM into CONFIG_DRM_LEGACY

CONFIG_DRM_VM gets selected by CONFIG_DRM_LEGACY, but nothing else. So
remove it and build drm_vm.o as part of CONFIG_DRM_LEGACY.

